item.how_to_find_us: Go up driveway with Meetup sign at the end (directly across from mailbox #298). Enter in front door with Meetup sign, and go on downstairs. Do NOT park in second driveway (which has "ULCS Clinic" sign.
item.why: We will be viewing and discussing a DVD presentation of recently translated info from the MCEO Guardian Alliance. This includes pre-ancient history and causes of cosmic energetic changes occuring in 2012. Keylontic science terms are used at times.
